text: Ilmetovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Aksaitovsky Selsoviet, Tatyshlinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 380 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 18 km from Verkhniye Tatyshly, 2 km from Aksaitovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Tatyshlinsky District
title: Ilmetovo
